'''约瑟夫·高桥'''（{{lang-en|Joseph S. Takahashi}}，{{bd|1951年|12月16日||}}），[[日裔美國人|日裔美国]][[遗传学家|遗传学家]]和[[神经生物学家|神经生物学家]]，{{link-en|德克萨斯大学西南医学中心|University of Texas Southwestern Medical Center}}教授和[[霍华德·休斯医学研究所|霍华德·休斯医学研究所]]研究人员。<ref name="NU">{{cite web|url=http://www.utsouthwestern.edu/findfac/professional/0,2356,105885,00.html |title=Neurobiology faculty - Joseph Takahashi |publisher=UT southwest |accessdate=2009-04-27}}</ref><ref name="HHMI bio">{{cite web|url=http://www.hhmi.org/research/investigators/takahashi_bio.html |title=HHMI Scientist Biography - Joseph Takahashi |publisher=Howard Hughes Medical Institute |accessdate=2009-04-24}}</ref>高桥的课题组于1994年发现了[[哺乳动物|哺乳动物]][[生物钟|生物钟]]的遗传学基础，在1997年确定出{{link-en|CLOCK基因|CLOCK}}<ref>{{Cite news|title=Gene Discovered in Mice that Regulates Biological Clock |publisher=Chicago Tribune |date=April 29, 1994}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/1994/04/29/us/found-in-mouse-the-gene-of-a-night-owl.html |title=Found in Mouse: The Gene of a Night Owl |publisher=The New York Times |date=April 29, 1994}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/1997/05/16/us/a-mouse-helps-explain-what-makes-us-tick.html?sec=health&spon=&pagewanted=2 |title=A Mouse Helps Explain What Makes Us Tick |first=Nicholas |last=Wade |date=May 16, 1997 |publisher=The New York Times}}</ref>。高桥于2003年当选为[[美国科学院|美国科学院]]院士<ref name="PNAS bio"/>。

==生平==
高桥1970年升入[[斯沃斯莫爾學院|斯沃斯莫爾學院]]，1974年获得生物学学士学位<ref name="PNAS bio">{{Cite journal|first=Melissa |last=Marino |title=Biography of Joseph S. Takahashi |journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences |doi= 10.1073/pnas.0401895101 |date=April 13, 2004 |volume=101 |issue=15 |pages=5336–5338|pmid=15067124|pmc=399313}}</ref>。随后，他进入 [[南卡罗来纳大学|南卡罗来纳大学]]以[[时间生物学|时间生物学]]研究见长的{{link-en|帕特丽夏·德库西|Patricia DeCoursey}}的课题组工作了一年，然后向[[德克萨斯州大学奥斯汀分校|德克萨斯州大学奥斯汀分校]]的{{link-en|迈克尔·梅纳克|Michael Menaker}}申请工作机会，梅纳克也是时间生物学领域的专家。梅纳克转赴[[俄勒岡大学|俄勒岡大学]]任教，高桥随之，并于1981年获得神经科学博士学位<ref name="PNAS bio"/>。获得博士学位后，高桥在{{link-en|美国国立精神卫生研究院|National Institute of Mental Health}}做了两年博士后，随后在 [[西北大学|西北大学]]神经科学和生理学系获得教职，后来，他在这里获得永久职位，并工作了26年<ref name="PNAS bio"/> 。2008年，高桥加入{{link-en|德克萨斯大学西南医学中心|University of Texas Southwestern Medical Center}}，任桑兹神经科学杰出讲席教授（Loyd B. Sands Distinguished Chair in Neuroscience）<ref name="NU"/>，同时任Hypnion公司科学顾问，这家公司主要业务是开发影响睡眠、睡醒和生物钟紊乱的中枢神经系统疾病的创新疗法<ref>{{cite web|title=Hypnion, Inc. Raises $10.4 Million In Series A Private Equity Financing|url=http://www.hypnion.com/about/news.htm|publisher=Hypnion, Inc.|accessdate=14 April 2011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110910063107/http://www.hypnion.com/about/news.htm|archive-date=2011-09-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。高桥还是《[[神经元（期刊）|神经元]]》、《生理基因组学》、《生物节律学报》等著名学术期刊的编委<ref>{{cite web|title=Joseph S. Takahashi Ph.D.|url=http://investing.businessweek.com/research/stocks/private/person.asp?personId=23377793&privcapId=124545&previousCapId=124545&previousTitle=Hypnion,%20Inc.|publisher=Businessweek|accessdate=14 April 2011}}</ref>。

==学术研究==

===生理起搏器视交叉上核（SCN）的研究===

1980年代初，高桥和梅纳克以试管内鸟[[松果体|松果体]]为研究对象，以研究昼夜节律振荡，他们证明哺乳动物的昼夜节律控制中心[[下丘脑|下丘脑]]的{{link-en|视交叉上核|suprachiasmatic nucleus}}（SCN），<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Takahashi |first1=J. S. |last2=Hamm |first2=H. |last3=Menaker |first3=M. |year=1980 |journal=Proc. Natl. Acad. Sci. |volume=77 |pages=2319–2322 |title=Circadian rhythms of melatonin release from individual superfused chicken pineal glands in vitro|doi=10.1073/pnas.77.4.2319|pmid=6929552|issue=4|pmc=348706}}</ref>在鸟类动物中有相同的作用<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Takahashi |first1=J. S. |last2=Menaker |first2=M. |year=1982 |journal=Journal of Neuroscience |volume=2 |pages=718–726}}</ref>。他们与德库西合作，以仓鼠做实验，证明了负责调控昼夜节律的感光系统与视觉系统不同<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Takahashi |first1=J. S. |last2=DeCoursey |first2=P. J. |last3=Bauman |first3=L. |last4=Menaker |first4=M. |year=1984 |journal=Nature |issue= 5955|pages=186–188 |title=Spectral sensitivity of a novel photoreceptive system mediating entrainment of mammalian circadian rhythms |pmid=6700721 |volume=308|doi=10.1038/308186a0}}</ref>。

2010年，高桥与人合作，研究了调控生物振荡的温度涨落的潜在作用。他们发现，主生理起搏器通常只受环境明暗循环调控，但分离在试管后，还能受到温度涨落的调控，这表明温度复位是所有哺乳动物的生物钟的重要性质，很可能在哺乳动物所有细胞中，通过一个非常保守的机制起作用，这也说明，全身组织的体温节律是主生物钟与昼夜节律同步的一个可能机制<ref name=temp>{{cite journal|last1=Buhr|first1=ED|last2=Yoo|first2=SH|last3=Takahashi|first3=JS|title=Temperature as a universal resetting cue for mammalian circadian oscillators|journal=Science|date=October 2010|volume=330|pages=379–85|doi=10.1126/science.1195262|issue=6002|pmid= 20947768}}</ref>。

===哺乳动物生物钟基因的节律性质研究===

高桥的研究给促进人对哺乳动物生物钟对生理学与环境关系的研究。1993年，高桥与{{link-en|迈克尔·格林伯格|Michael E. Greenberg}}合作，研究了哺乳动物视交叉上核受环境光循环交叉的调控，研究了{{link-en|环磷腺苷效应元件结合蛋白|CREB}}和''[[c-fos|c-fos]]''蛋白转录之间的关系<!--后者曾被认为是光诱导路径的成分 transcription, a protein previously indicated as a component of the photic entrainment pathway.--><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Kornhauser |first1=J.M. |last2=Nelson |first2=D.E. |last3=Mayo |first3=K.E. |last4=Takahashi |first4=J.S. |year=1990 |journal=Neuron |volume=5 |pages=127–134 |title=Photic and circadian regulation of c-fos gene expression in the hamster suprachiasmatic nucleus|doi=10.1016/0896-6273(90)90303-W|pmid=2116813|issue=2}}</ref>。借助[[免疫沉淀法|免疫沉淀法]]，高桥和格林伯格证明了光致CREB磷酸化作用只在夜晚发生<ref name="ReferenceA">{{cite journal|last1=Ginty |first1=D.D |last2=Kornhauser |first2=J.M. |last3=Thompson |first3=M.A. |last4=Bading |first4=H. |last5=Mayo |first5=K.E. |last6=Takahashi |first6=J.S. |last7=Greenberg |first7=M.E. |year=1993 |journal=Science |volume=260 |pages=238–241 |title=Regulation of CREB Phosphorylation in the Suprachiasmatic Nucleus by Light and a Circadian Clock|doi=10.1126/science.8097062|pmid=8097062|issue=5105}}</ref>。<!-- Given that CREB has been shown to regulate ''c-fos'' transcription in [[PC12_cells|PC12]] pheochromocytoma cells,<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Sheng |first1=M. |last2=Thompson |first2=M.A. |last3=Greenberg |first3=M.E. |year=1991 |journal=Science |volume=252 |pages=1427–1430 |title=CREB: a Ca(2+)-regulated transcription factor phosphorylated by calmodulin-dependent kinases|doi=10.1126/science.1646483|pmid=1646483|issue=5011}}</ref> Takahashi and Greenberg were able to conclude that phosphorylation of CREB in the SCN may play an important role in mammalian photic entrainment.<ref name="ReferenceA"/>-->

松果体体外研究有着明显的局限性，高桥利用{{link-en|正向遗传学|forward genetics}}和[[定位克隆|定位克隆]]技术研究昼夜节律的遗传和分子基础<ref name="PNAS bio"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://nrc88.nas.edu/pnas_search/memberDetails.aspx?ctID=20004791 |title=PNAS Member Editor - Joseph Takahashi |publisher=Proceedings of the National Academy of Science |accessdate=2009-04-28}}</ref>。1994年，高桥及其同事分离出了{{link-en|CLOCK基因|CLOCK}}<ref name="1994 Science">{{cite journal|last1=Vitaterna |first1=M.H. |first2=D.P. |last2=King |first3=A.M. |last3=Chang |first4=J.M. |last4=Kornhauser |first5=P.L. |last5=Lowrey |first6=J.D. |last6=McDonald |first7=W.F. |last7=Dove |first8=L.H. |last8=Pinto |first9=F.W. |last9=Turek |last10= Takahashi|first10=J.S.|year=1994|title=Mutagenesis and mapping of a mouse gene, Clock, essential for circadian behavior |journal=Science |issue= 5159|pages=719–725 |pmid=8171325 |doi=10.1126/science.8171325 |volume=264}}</ref>，1997年，他们克隆出了哺乳动物的CLOCK基因<ref name="PNAS bio"/><ref name="Cell 1997a">{{cite journal|first1=David |last1=King |first2=Yaliang |last2=Zhao |first3=Ashvin |last3=Sangoram |first4=Lisa |last4=Wilsbacher |first5=Monuru |last5=Tanaka |first6=Marina |last6=Antoch |first7=Thomas |last7=Steeves |first10=Phillip |last10=Lowrey |first11=Fred |last11=Turek |title=Positional Cloning of the Mouse Circadian ''Clock'' Gene |journal=Cell |volume=89 |pages=641–653 |year=1997|doi=10.1016/S0092-8674(00)80245-7|pmid=9160755|last8=Vitaterna|last9=Kornhauser|last12=Takahashi |first12=J.S.|issue=4}}</ref>。

2000年，高桥克隆出了1988年就被发现的''tau''基因，他称此为自己最重大的科学成就之一<ref name="PNAS bio" />。高桥发现，该基因与果蝇''dbt''基因和人类''CKIe''基因密切相关<ref>{{cite web|title=Joseph S. Takahashi, Ph.D.|url=http://www.hhmi.org/biointeractive/clocks/takahashi.html|publisher=hhmi|accessdate=14 April 2011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121007210621/http://www.hhmi.org/biointeractive/clocks/takahashi.html|archive-date=2012-10-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。
